  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589650/extras/c3494d0ab4f088a4494967fdea0af4b6.avif?t=1708032932\" width=558 height=168 /></span><br>A simple puzzle game in which you restore colourful pictures that have been shattered into clusters of triangles.<br>Watch the sharp-looking polygons turn into more recognizable and pleasant sights at the flick of your mouse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589650/extras/05e84cdafaa5e1bdebba2665b7347978.poster.avif?t=1708032932\" width=540 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589650/extras/05e84cdafaa5e1bdebba2665b7347978.webm?t=1708032932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589650/extras/05e84cdafaa5e1bdebba2665b7347978.mp4?t=1708032932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hundreds of puzzles to complete<br></li><li>Pleasing, colourful artworks<br></li><li>Calm, ambient music and sound<br></li><li>Points for fast completion<br></li><li>Light and dark mode</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589650/extras/c3494d0ab4f088a4494967fdea0af4b6.avif?t=1708032932\" width=558 height=168 /></span><br>A simple puzzle game in which you restore colourful pictures that have been shattered into clusters of triangles.<br>Watch the sharp-looking polygons turn into more recognizable and pleasant sights at the flick of your mouse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589650/extras/05e84cdafaa5e1bdebba2665b7347978.poster.avif?t=1708032932\" width=540 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589650/extras/05e84cdafaa5e1bdebba2665b7347978.webm?t=1708032932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2589650/extras/05e84cdafaa5e1bdebba2665b7347978.mp4?t=1708032932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hundreds of puzzles to complete<br></li><li>Pleasing, colourful artworks<br></li><li>Calm, ambient music and sound<br></li><li>Points for fast completion<br></li><li>Light and dark mode</li></ul>",
